Response object returned from time lookup service. success boolean should be checked to verify time was found successfully. In case of error, messages will be in the error message.

  • delvDate character alphanumeric to display delivery date
  • delvTime character alphanumeric to display delivery time
  • delvDay character alphanumeric to display delivery day
  • orgSrvCntr character alphanumeric to display origin service center
  • destSrvCntr character alphanumeric to display destination service center
  • message character alphanumeric to display error message
  • success boolean True if Found, False if not
